1955
01:32:16,369 --> 01:32:20,205
♪ I was made for loving you, baby ♪

1956
01:32:20,306 --> 01:32:23,879
♪ You were made for loving me ♪

1957
01:32:23,980 --> 01:32:25,682
♪ I can't get enough ♪

1958
